ata records in the early stage of COVID-19 outbreaks, where the\nresults demonstrate the efficiency and effectiveness of C-Watcher for early\ndetection of high-risk neighborhoods from a large number of cities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Dec 2020 17:02:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 Jan 2021 17:05:47 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 4 Mar 2021 19:02:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-08"}
