t of substructures in the\nshape of stars, we explicitly show that their contribution is subdominant.\nOverlaying our theoretical results to the observational constraints from\nprevious literature, we establish fair agreement.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Dec 2020 19:00:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 5 Jun 2021 15:46:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-08"}
