wer to pick up the increase in the case numbers\nin September 2020 but forecasting improves again in the later stages of the\nepidemic.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Dec 2020 22:27:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-24"}
